title: Tree shears capacity to fell 300mm diameter trees
summary: Grip and hold shear harvester head for trees minimum of 300mm.

eligible.eligibleBullet02: grip and hold trees of at least 300mm in diameter
eligible.eligibleBullet03: shear cut trees of at least 300mm in diameter
eligible.eligibleText01: Tree shears which use saw blades to cut the tree are not eligible under this item.
